product.longDescription: A unique and delicious addition to salad mix. Very deeply incised, so cut heads create uniformly thin leaflets. Maintains head shape after harvest and washing which makes it suitable for whole-head sales. Leaves have a nice iceberg texture and excellent, complex flavor. Great paired with our Salanova® lettuce types. High resistance to downy mildew races EU 16, 18, 21–26, 32. MT0-30. Avg. 302,000 seeds/lb. Packet: 25 seeds.
product.shortDescription: Distinctive, highly textured, one-cut type. Conventional seed with NOP-compliant pelleting.
